  12,42,"And he said to the one whom he knew to be saved: "
  13,7,"And the disbelievers say: "
  13,8,"Allâh knows what every female bears, and by how much the wombs fall short (of their time or number) or exceed. Everything with Him is in (due) proportion."
  13,9,"All-Knower of the Unseen and the seen, the Most Great, the Most High."